Pre-Requisite(s) Spell Casting Fury <br>
Level Requirement: 59 <br>
Ability Type: Passive  <br>
Max Training: 3 Levels <br>
Point Cost: Level 1: 3 points<br>
Level 2: 6 points<br>
Level 3: 9 points <br>
Description: This spell reduces the casting time on Direct Damage spells.<br>
The amount of time reduced is 2%, 5% and 10% of the spells casting time based on the number of points invested.<br>
<br>
There is a pre-requisite of 3 points spent in Spell Casting Fury for this ability.<br>
 <br>
Both Wizards and Druids get this ability yet we do not? I've been wondering about this for a very long time and now that we have reclaimed our title as second best nuker I really don't understand why we don't have this AA.  We could really use some decent class AA badly and I think this would be a step in the right direction.  Let me know what you think. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=29211"><br>
